OL,7,Ffor people suffering psychological
OL,8,Fharm should also be scrapped,
OL,9,Faccording to the review, as should the
OL,10,Fpractice of a claim dying with the
OL,11,Fclaimant.
OL,13,FSir Brian also recommends the system
OL,14,Fensures "as many people as possible
OL,15,Freceive some compensation in their
OL,16,Flifetime".
