OL,6,FVictims of the Infected Blood Scandal
OL,7,Ftold ITV News a year after the scheme
OL,8,Fwas established that they were in the
OL,9,Fdark about when they could receive
OL,10,Fcompensation, and feared they would
OL,11,Fdie before they saw justice.
OL,13,FRichard Warwick was a student at Lord
OL,14,FMayor's Treloar's College, a boarding
OL,15,Fschool for children with disabilities,
OL,16,Fwhich had a specialist NHS haemophilia
OL,17,Fcentre on site.
