OL,6,FIt was there boys with haemophilia
OL,7,Freceived factor 8 treatment, some of
OL,8,Fit made from blood donated by groups
OL,9,Fat high risk of HIV and hepatitis,
OL,10,Fincluding drug addicts and prisoners
OL,11,Fin America.
OL,13,FIn total 122 boys contracted HIV or
OL,14,FHepatitis C. Richard contracted both.
OL,15,FFewer than 20 survived.
OL,17,FRichard has received an invitation to
OL,18,Fthe compensation scheme and an interim
OL,19,Fpayment, but is still waiting for the
OL,20,Ffull amount.
