OL,6,FHe says he thinks the delays are the
OL,7,FGovernment playing for time: "We've
OL,8,Fbeen promised the earth and we've been
OL,9,Feffectively given very little in
OL,10,Freturn.
OL,12,F"They seem to be capitulating, and it
OL,13,Falmost seems as if they're waiting for
OL,14,Fmore and more people to die so they'll
OL,15,Fhave less and less to pay out."
OL,17,F"The people that are infected, are
OL,18,Fregistered and already on the schemes.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/17
