OL,6,F"All their medical knowledge about
OL,7,Fthem is known about. The conditions
OL,8,Fare known about, the dates of
OL,9,Finfections are known about. They
OL,10,Fshould be passported immediately
OL,11,Fthrough the system and paid."
OL,13,FPaymaster General Nick Thomas-Symonds
OL,14,Fapologised to victims, and said the
OL,15,FGovernment is "not dragging our
