OL,6,F"When I gave evidence to Sir Brian's
OL,7,Finquiry, I said quite clearly that
OL,8,Fthere were other areas that I was
OL,9,Fwilling to look at," said Thomas-
OL,10,FSymonds.
OL,12,F"And that is precisely what I will do.
OL,13,FI will once again reflect. But I am
OL,14,Falso determined I will not allow
OL,15,Ffurther undue delay in people
OL,16,Freceiving their compensation."
