OL,6,FDes Collins, senior partner at Collins
OL,7,FSolicitors and adviser to 1,500
OL,8,Fvictims of the scandal, said: "In our
OL,9,Fview there has already been some
OL,10,Frecent progress in the number of
OL,11,Finfected people being invited to apply
OL,12,Ffor compensation.
OL,14,F"However it remains the case that
OL,15,Fthose affected - by virtue of the fact
OL,16,Fthey lost husbands, fathers, sons and
OL,17,Ffamily members to infected blood/blood
OL,18,Fproducts - are still in the dark about
OL,19,Fthe route to compensation for them.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/17
