OL,6,F"There has been absolutely no guidance
OL,7,Fon timeframes for when they will be
OL,8,Finvited to apply - these members of
OL,9,Fthe community deserve better.
OL,11,F"Whilst the path to compensation for
OL,12,Fthe infected blood community has been
OL,13,Ffar from smooth, improvements can
OL,14,Fstill be made."
OL,16,FSpeaking as the report was published,
OL,17,Fthe chairman of the Infected Blood
OL,18,FInquiry said delay in providing
OL,19,Fcompensation to victims has created
OL,20,F"an injustice all of its own".
