OL,6,FSir Brian Langstaff said:
OL,7,F"Compensation needed to be rolled out
OL,8,Fquickly.
OL,10,F"Time has always been an enemy. Some
OL,11,Ftime may have to be taken to get
OL,12,Fthings right - but time should never
OL,13,Fbe allowed to become delay. Delay
OL,14,Fcreates an injustice all of its own.
