OL,6,FHe added that the expert group tasked
OL,7,Fwith advising the Government on the
OL,8,Fschemes design "was specifically
OL,9,Fforbidden by its terms of reference
OL,10,Ffrom talking to people infected and
OL,11,Faffected, the very people with the
OL,12,Fclosest, most intimate knowledge and
OL,13,Funderstanding of what the compensation
OL,14,Fscheme was supposed to compensate".
OL,16,F"It should have been unthinkable to
OL,17,Fdesign a scheme without properly
OL,18,Finvolving people affected by the
OL,19,Fdecisions being taken by the
OL,20,FGovernment."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/17
