OL,6,FSpeaking ahead of the publication of
OL,7,Fthe new Inquiry report, Kate Burt,
OL,8,Fchief executive of the Haemophilia
OL,9,FSociety, said: "Delays and uncertainty
OL,10,Fabout compensation continue to have a
OL,11,Fdevastating mental and physical impact
OL,12,Fon the infected blood community.
OL,14,F"We hope the Infected Blood Inquiry's
OL,15,Freport on the government's handling of
OL,16,Fcompensation will help to resolve
OL,17,Fremaining concerns about the scheme as
OL,18,Fwell as maintain pressure to deliver
OL,19,Ffair payments as quickly as possible."
